        "children": [
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "Instead of the owner of the C7 Corvette having to call OnStar or the authorities having to do it, the security system in the sports car automatically recognized it had been boosted and contacted the OnStar call center, which ",
