      {
        "children": [
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "Hilariously, the local news report made OnStar’s ability to shut down a vehicle remotely sound like some barely-released, new-fangled technology. Just wait until they learn about key fob spoofing and vehicle lane assist systems.",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
          }
        ],
        "direction": "ltr",
        "format": "",
        "indent": 0,
        "type": "paragraph",
        "version": 1
      },
      {
        "children": [
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "As the local news pointed out, the risk of police chasing a high-performance car being driven by a motivated suspect is that a ",
